@meta
title: Postmortem - Payment Approval Timeout
version: 0.1
owner: platform-pay

@map
- PM-001 | Incident Summary | Record incident duration and user impact in one place
- PM-010 | Timeline | Keep high-signal, time-ordered event history
- PM-015 | Decision Chain and Assumptions | Restore key decisions and assumptions to trace repeat failure patterns
- PM-020 | Root Cause Analysis | Focus on causes, not only symptoms
- PM-030 | Response Review | Keep balanced review for team learning
- PM-040 | Prevention Actions | Define owner and due date for each action item
- PM-050 | Source Feedback Completion | Require source-doc feedback evidence before closing postmortem

@section PM-001
title: Incident Summary
summary: Record incident duration and user impact in one place
links: INCIDENT-001
content:
<<<
[Incident window]
- Start:
- End:

[Impact]
- User-facing impact:
- Estimated affected users:
>>>

@section PM-010
title: Timeline
summary: Keep high-signal, time-ordered event history
links: LOG-001
content:
<<<
00:00 - First alert
00:00 - On-call acknowledged
00:00 - Investigation started
00:00 - Mitigation applied
00:00 - Recovery confirmed
>>>

@section PM-015
title: Decision Chain and Assumptions
summary: Restore key decisions and assumptions to trace repeat failure patterns
links: DECISION-TRACE-CHK
content:
<<<
- Record decision, evidence, approver, and failed assumptions
>>>

@section PM-020
title: Root Cause Analysis
summary: Focus on causes, not only symptoms
links: PR-001
content:
<<<
