2)
>>>

@section PM-040
title: Prevention Actions
summary: Define owner and due date for each action item
links: ACTION-BOARD-001
content:
<<<
1) Action: / Owner: / Due:
2) Action: / Owner: / Due:
3) Action: / Owner: / Due:
>>>

@section PM-050
title: Source Feedback Completion
summary: Require source-doc feedback evidence before closing postmortem
links: SOURCE-FEEDBACK-CHK
content:
<<<
- Record source doc, section, change ID, and completion date
>>>

